{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 1.\tx360\tab MODE 1: All tracks\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 2.\tx360\tab MODE 2: Only selected tracks\line \line If you don't select any tracks, MODE 1 will be engaged automatically. On the other hand, as soon as any number of tracks are selected, MODE 2 will kick in.\sa180\par}
